---
title: Euro-Inspired Chorizo Wraps with Creamy Feta Sauce and Sweet Pepper Spread
description: Meet our quick and easy version of 'cevapi', a grilled meat wrap hailing from the Balkan region of Europe. Flush with green lettuce mix and a creamy feta spread, it's every bit as filling as it is delicious!
